snippet.title: Space Boat Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: This is the first glimpse of Space Boat, an investigative narrative adventure set on an intergalactic cruise-ship inhabited by various carpet-based lifeforms. Play as a cleverly disguised space cat, traverse the perils of time and space, and track down an elusive shape-shifting jewel thief before it's too late!
